    <span class="badge-primary mb-2">Athletic & Sports</span>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
      Basketball Shoes Guide
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600">
      Everything you need to know about basketball shoes: from high-top ankle support to advanced cushioning technologies. Find the perfect basketball footwear for your game.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Featured Image -->
  <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
